1→import * as THREE from "three";
     2→import "./style.css";
     3→import { OrbitControls } from "three/examples/jsm/controls/OrbitControls.js";
     4→import { GLTFLoader } from 'three/examples/jsm/loaders/GLTFLoader.js'
     5→import { DRACOLoader } from 'three/examples/jsm/loaders/DRACOLoader.js'
     6→import firefliesVertexShader from './shaders/fireflies/vertex.glsl'
     7→import firefliesFragmentShader from './shaders/fireflies/fragment.glsl'
     8→
     9→
    10→const debugObject = {};
    11→
    12→// Canvas
    13→const canvas = document.querySelector("canvas.webgl");
    14→
    15→
    16→// Sizes
    17→const sizes = {
    18→  width: window.innerWidth,
    19→  height: window.innerHeight,
    20→};
    21→
    22→// Scene
    23→const scene = new THREE.Scene();
    24→
    25→const geometry = new THREE.BoxGeometry(1, 1, 1);
    26→const material = new THREE.MeshBasicMaterial({ color: 0x00ff00 });
    27→const cube = new THREE.Mesh(geometry, material);
    28→cube.position.x = -3
    29→scene.add(cube);
    30→
    31→/**
    32→ * Fireflies
    33→ */
    34→// Geometry
    35→const firefliesGeometry = new THREE.BufferGeometry()
    36→const firefliesCount = 30
    37→const positionArray = new Float32Array(firefliesCount * 3)
    38→const scaleArray = new Float32Array(firefliesCount)
    39→
    40→for(let i = 0; i < firefliesCount; i++)
    41→{
    42→    positionArray[i * 3 + 0] = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 4
    43→    positionArray[i * 3 + 1] = Math.random() * 1.5
    44→    positionArray[i * 3 + 2] = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 4
    45→
    46→    scaleArray[i] = Math.random()
    47→}
    48→
    49→firefliesGeometry.setAttribute('position', new THREE.BufferAttribute(positionArray, 3))
    50→firefliesGeometry.setAttribute('aScale', new THREE.BufferAttribute(scaleArray, 1))
    51→
    52→// Material
    53→const firefliesMaterial = new THREE.ShaderMaterial({
    54→    uniforms:
    55→    {
    56→        uTime: { value: 0 },
    57→        uPixelRatio: { value: Math.min(window.devicePixelRatio, 2) },
    58→        uSize: { value: 100 }
    59→    },
    60→    vertexShader: firefliesVertexShader,
    61→    fragmentShader: firefliesFragmentShader,
    62→    transparent: true,
    63→    blending: THREE.AdditiveBlending,
    64→    depthWrite: false
    65→})
    66→
    67→// Points
    68→const fireflies = new THREE.Points(firefliesGeometry, firefliesMaterial)
    69→fireflies.position.x = 3
    70→scene.add(fireflies)
    71→
    72→
    73→/**
    74→ * Models
    75→ */
    76→const dracoLoader = new DRACOLoader()
    77→dracoLoader.setDecoderPath('/draco/')
    78→
    79→const gltfLoader = new GLTFLoader()
    80→gltfLoader.setDRACOLoader(dracoLoader)
    81→
    82→let mixer = null
    83→gltfLoader.load(
    84→    '/models/Fox/glTF/Fox.gltf',
    85→    (gltf) =>
    86→    {
    87→        gltf.scene.scale.set(0.025, 0.025, 0.025)
    88→        scene.add(gltf.scene)
    89→
    90→        // Animation
    91→        mixer = new THREE.AnimationMixer(gltf.scene)
    92→        const action = mixer.clipAction(gltf.animations[2])
    93→        action.play()
    94→    }
    95→)
    96→
    97→
    98→/**
    99→ * Lights
   100→ */
   101→const ambientLight = new THREE.AmbientLight(0xffffff, 2.4)
   102→scene.add(ambientLight)
   103→
   104→/**
   105→ * Camera
   106→ */
   107→const camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera(45, sizes.width / sizes.height, 0.1, 100)
   108→camera.position.z = 10;
   109→
   110→/**
   111→ * Sizes
   112→ */
   113→window.addEventListener("resize", () => {
   114→  // Update sizes
   115→  sizes.width = window.innerWidth;
   116→  sizes.height = window.innerHeight;
   117→
   118→  // Update camera
   119→  camera.aspect = sizes.width / sizes.height;
   120→  camera.updateProjectionMatrix();
   121→
   122→  // Update renderer
   123→  renderer.setSize(sizes.width, sizes.height);
   124→  renderer.setPixelRatio(Math.min(window.devicePixelRatio, 2));
   125→
   126→  // Update fireflies
   127→  firefliesMaterial.uniforms.uPixelRatio.value = Math.min(window.devicePixelRatio, 2)
   128→});
   129→
   130→
   131→// Controls
   132→const controls = new OrbitControls(camera, canvas);
   133→controls.enableDamping = true;
   134→
   135→/**
   136→ * Renderer
   137→ */
   138→const renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({
   139→  canvas: canvas,
   140→  antialias: true,
   141→});
   142→renderer.setSize(sizes.width, sizes.height);
   143→renderer.setPixelRatio(Math.min(window.devicePixelRatio, 2));
   144→
   145→debugObject.clearColor = "#201919";
   146→renderer.setClearColor(debugObject.clearColor);
   147→
   148→/**
   149→ * Animate
   150→ */
   151→let previousTime = 0
   152→const clock = new THREE.Clock();
   153→
   154→function animate() {
   155→  const elapsedTime = clock.getElapsedTime();
   156→
   157→  cube.rotation.x += 0.01;
   158→  cube.rotation.y += 0.01;
   159→
   160→  const deltaTime = elapsedTime - previousTime
   161→  previousTime = elapsedTime
   162→
   163→  // Model animation
   164→  if(mixer)
   165→  {
   166→      mixer.update(deltaTime)
   167→  }
   168→
   169→   // Particles animation
   170→  firefliesMaterial.uniforms.uTime.value = elapsedTime
   171→
   172→  // Update controls
   173→  controls.update();
   174→
   175→  // Render
   176→  renderer.render(scene, camera);
   177→  // Call tick again on the next frame
   178→  window.requestAnimationFrame(animate);
   179→}
   180→animate();
